name: Roma2lug bot
body:
### Welcome to the Roma2Lug Telegram BOT.
This bot is meant to automate the assistance that our organization recieves from university students.
If you want to use this project feel free to use it as you like, just give a little comment or credit to Roma2Lug and Krajetum.

***
Hail to the Open Source.

### Authors and Contributors
Author Lorenzo Licalzi (@Krajetum).
